OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be partly cloudy with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, heavy at first. Then the rest
OL,8,Fof the night will see variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud and some showery rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,12,Fthrough the day and a scattering of
OL,13,Fshowers, these heavy in the north.
OL,14,FBecoming drier through the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,17,Fon Thursday morning, and again later
OL,18,Fin the day. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,19,FFriday. Chance of some rain at first
OL,20,Fon Saturday, otherwise mainly dry.
OL,21,FWarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
